  "title": "Convergence with Armen Panossian, Raghav Khanna, and Danielle Poli",
  "body": "<html><body><div class=\"node__content\"> <section class=\"detail-page-head full-width-block\"><div class=\"container medium\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-12\"> <small>Oaktree Capital- <span class=\"field field--name-created field--type-created field--label-hidden\"><time class=\"datetime\" datetime=\"2025-11-24T21:33:17+00:00\" title=\"Monday, November 24, 2025 - 21:33\">Mon, 11/24/2025 - 21:33</time></span></small><h1><span class=\"field field--name-title field--type-string field--label-hidden\">Convergence with Armen Panossian, Raghav Khanna, and Danielle Poli</span></h1></div></div></div> </section> <section class=\"detail-page additional-height\"><div class=\"container medium\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-8-lg\"><div class=\"feature-image-visability\"><div class=\"field field--name-field-banner field--type-entity-reference field--label-hidden field__item\"><article class=\"media media--type-image media--view-mode-default insurance-library-image\"><div class=\"field field--name-field-media-image field--type-image field--label-visually_hidden\"><div class=\"field__label visually-hidden\">Image</div><div class=\"field__item\"> <img alt=\"OaktreeFeatured\" class=\"lazyload img-fluid\" data-src=\"/sites/default/files/2025-11/OaktreeFeatured_1.jpg\" height=\"422\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"/sites/default/files/2025-11/OaktreeFeatured_1.jpg\" width=\"1004\"/></div></div> </article></div></div><div class=\"audio-player\"></div><p>How are private and liquid credit evolving into complementary forces? And how can combining these two distinct but interlinked markets be of benefit to both investors and issuers? In an in-depth conversation, Armen Panossian (Co-CEO and Head of Performing Credit), Raghav Khanna (Co-Portfolio Manager, Strategic Credit), and Danielle Poli (Assistant Portfolio Manager, Global Credit) discuss the implications of the liquid-private credit convergence.</p><p><audio controls=\"\" style=\"width:100%;\"> <source src=\"/sites/default/files/2025-11/Insight%20Podcast%20-%20Liquid-Private%20Credit%20Convergence.mp3\" style=\"width:100%\" type=\"audio/mpeg\"> </source></audio></p><p><a class=\"btn btn-tritory\" href=\"/oaktree-capital-management-lp\">Read More from Oaktree Capital Management</a></p><div class=\"avalible-pods\"><div class=\"block block-block-content block-block-content9a03abe3-6e62-4857-9ccf-a8978d7294f7\" id=\"block-podcastisavailableon\"><div class=\"field field--name-field-link-with-image field--type-entity-reference-revisions field--label-hidden field__items\"><div class=\"field__item\"><h3>The InsuranceAUM.com podcast is available on</h3><div class=\"btns-wrapper\"> <a aria-label=\"extrerbal-link\" href=\"https://open.spotify.com/show/6WIbsYrL1BXuJMPsZXSk8R\" target=\"_blank\"> <img alt=\"\" height=\"52px\" src=\"/sites/default/files/2023-08/btn2.png\" width=\"200px\"/></a> <a aria-label=\"extrerbal-link\" href=\"https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/insuranceaum-com/id1500643401\" target=\"_blank\"> <img alt=\"\" height=\"52px\" src=\"/sites/default/files/2023-08/btn3.png\" width=\"200px\"/></a> <a aria-label=\"extrerbal-link\" href=\"https://www.amazon.com/InsuranceAUM-com/dp/B08K57V1D6\" target=\"_blank\"> <img alt=\"\" height=\"52px\" src=\"/sites/default/files/2025-03/Frame%20366%20%281%29.png\" width=\"200px\"/></a> <a aria-label=\"extrerbal-link\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/@InsuranceAUMCommunity\" target=\"_blank\"> <img alt=\"\" height=\"52px\" src=\"/sites/default/files/2025-03/frame_366%20%281%29%20%281%29.png\" width=\"200px\"/></a></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"col-4-lg\"><div class=\"addtoany-social-icons mb-3\"><div class=\"addtoany-social-icons mb-3\"><h4>Share this post</h4> <span class=\"a2a_kit a2a_kit_size_32 addtoany_list d-flex gap-2 justify-content-start\" data-a2a-title=\"Convergence with Armen Panossian, Raghav Khanna, and Danielle Poli\" data-a2a-url=\"https://insuranceaum.com/convergence-with-armen-panossian-raghav-khanna-and